    {
      "id": "capabilities-shared",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Shared Capabilities",
      "position": {
        "x": -120,
        "y": 20
      },
      "width": 420,
      "height": 1060,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Shared Capabilities\n\n### Planning\n- content\n- controls\n- semantic-zoom\n- prompt-extraction\n- relationship visibility\n\n### Knowledge / Research\n- content\n- references / citation surfaces\n- semantic-zoom\n- document-surface\n- relationship visibility\n\n### Agent / Prompting\n- content\n- controls\n- execution\n- prompt-extraction\n- navigation / handoff\n\n### Workflow / Execution\n- ports\n- execution\n- controls\n- state display\n- layout-sensitive\n\n### Repeaters across sets\n- `content`\n- `controls`\n- `semantic-zoom`\n- `prompt-extraction`\n\nThese repeated capabilities are probably substrate-level concerns.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
